{"tid":468043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啲廢中真係好撚鍾意單單打打","createTime":"2017-11-14T04:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T13:49:15.000Z","uid":390,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6cebf8c5e0fbd59de16a02baa4c4d12f6b720384","tid":468043,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:54:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱係屋企出門口，入電梯已經有兩公婆企咗喺左邊，咁我就企右邊。<br />\n<br />\n落咗幾層開門有個男人望住我，叫我地落去先，我已經㩒緊閂門，點知兩公婆話「唔緊要啦」。於是我諗緊應該係個男人拖住隻狗廢時同lift，驚有人唔鐘意。但我果個角度係見唔到有狗，我都係估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁都無計已經閂咗門，我即刻㩒開門但都開唔切，我就繼續㩒電話。點知兩公婆係到單單打打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老公=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老婆=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「有時啲人掛住睇自己嘢呢夾死人都唔知呀」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係囉」<br />\n其實我果陣一望出去就剩係望到個男人，佢叫我地落去先我咪潛意識關即時㩒閂門，因為我根本見唔到佢拖狗，係諗諗下先估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦咁串完我，佢地早我一層出，點知出去前仲要繼續講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「真係好唔好意思囉」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係囉唔知啲人有冇理人感受」<br />\n屌你老母啲語氣嘴臉好撚乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係！我係㩒電話無睇清楚，但個男人唔落我咪閂門囉！你兩公婆有手有腳唔阻止，走住黎屌？<br />\n我講左句：「我又唔係揸lift嘅⋯」<br />\n佢地睥一睥我就出咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲廢中就係鍾意玩批鬥<br />\n單單打打講說話你聽<br />\n仲要扮唔係同你講咁<br />\n做人做到咁真係好小家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/125218_4be35653829ed6b88ad63dd844a3a3e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F125218_4be35653829ed6b88ad63dd844a3a3e7.jpg&h=c816ea03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b43cd9c07048db24f32cb887525e092d5e5f89ed","tid":468043,"uid":73109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ac43b05ce8c238baf5d72b3df4e09449bdcda45","tid":468043,"uid":390,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私樓？</blockquote><br />\n唔好錯重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩樓都有呢啲閪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8495dede74fe70e75d4e0ec35692abe4bb7d793b","tid":468043,"uid":390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/130014_b353fcb10b84299adfdddd348b67ad56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F130014_b353fcb10b84299adfdddd348b67ad56.jpg&h=63a4ae9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推"},{"pid":"e99ddb2b84f1dff97c4067b613f5a59dafa5cb59","tid":468043,"uid":390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/130041_340f8cc45d9f336a25f701f98ff47c4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F130041_340f8cc45d9f336a25f701f98ff47c4b.jpg&h=12d6a756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26856cc62564f2e3605dfe3e5efd5e61b85153ae","tid":468043,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55aac3f3d15b9c0209b087a58f4a0175d29ab792","tid":468043,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40ba0544aa690d3bbe94946c04757c08adb6f5df","tid":468043,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>私樓？</blockquote><br />\n唔好錯重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩樓都有呢啲閪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n私樓串D</blockquote><br />\n都有好人㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似個狗主驚人唔鍾意所以叫我地落樓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc460fde2de34347d7455b9782640b5fd158083","tid":468043,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/132809_e15032a9a6b283fdb7f95d1340d644db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F132809_e15032a9a6b283fdb7f95d1340d644db.jpg&h=d391aff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b213cbec7efe3720aa74509bb962258d5ad96639","tid":468043,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dac04397c8d59067731cb8d3f5013afc8918be","tid":468043,"uid":311,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"負皮比Ali"}]}